official_title: Pilot of Lifestyle Behavior Intervention for Non-Alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease
inclusion_criteria:
* Self-reported Hispanic/Latino
* Have been diagnosed with NAFLD
* Able to speak English or Spanish
* Have access to internet, either on their phone, at home or at some other location convenient to the participant
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Does not have a working telephone number
